<page section="download">
  <heading>Download</heading>

  <content>
    <p>
      Go to <github-releases-stable /> and download <strong><workbench-download-file release="stable" wm="gtk" os="linux" arch="x86_64" /></strong>.
    </p>

    <div id="download-info">
      <img src="img/workbench-linux.png" class="pic" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;" alt="Carrot2 Clustering Workbench Download" />

      <strong>After download completes:</strong>

      <ol>
        <li>
          Extract the archive to some local directory
        </li>

        <li>
          Run <tt>carrot2-workbench</tt>
        </li>

        <li>
          Take a look at some <manual-link target="_blank" section="section.getting-started">common getting started scenarios</manual-link>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <p class="note">
        <strong>Note: </strong><c2 /> <dcw /> requires  <a
        href="http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp"
        target="_blank">Java Runtime Environment</a> (version 1.6.0 or later).
      </p>
    </div>
  </content>
</page>
